apologize before?

17:50.286 --> 17:52.071
Fix everything!
Cost nothing!

17:52.114 --> 17:53.420
Well, you have to mean it.

17:53.463 --> 17:55.248
Thorfinn not
like your hat!

17:55.291 --> 17:57.119
- Excuse me?
- Sorry. All good.

18:00.122 --> 18:02.429
Oh, Pete.

18:03.952 --> 18:05.954
